{"tid":811543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為多機跑分作弊卻回應：別的廠都是這樣做","createTime":"2018-09-09T02:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T15:06:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b416aa9491615ce6d75418ba8da58f419c29e23","tid":811543,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"華為多機跑分作弊卻回應：別的廠都是這樣做<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/09/08/huawei-cheat-for-benchmark/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2Fhuawei-cheat-for-benchmark%2F&d=Zdays%2Fva7Gj8FXNPFS381ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=99a9ce2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/09/08/huawei-cheat-for-benchmark/</a><br />\n<br />\n當今手機已成為不可缺少的工具，相信很多用戶購買手機時面對誇張的廣告並不賣賬，而是會看重對手機性能跑分。一些小廠商為了銷量也會選擇「作弊」&mdash;&mdash;偷偷修改跑分數據。近日，中國手機華為被爆出跑分作弊，一時間成為了輿論的焦點。<br />\n<br />\n近日，AnandTech 網站發現華為在 榮耀play 新機上動了手腳，一般來說，平時使用時手機的處理器會降頻以防止過熱和提高續航能力。而華為的做法則是測試跑分時在手機中加入了基準測試檢測機制，在某些被列入白名單的應用程序中讓 SoC 解鎖更高的功率限制，就是只要打開測試App 手機就會進行調節獲得比較高的跑分，這種做法有作弊的嫌疑。手機跑分提升，則意味著功耗方面會有所下降。<br />\n<br />\n針對此事，華為軟件總裁 Dr. Wang Chenglu 表示當下跑分測試越來越不能代表實際體驗，但目前大部分的評測都愛以跑分來標榜手機性能表現，榮耀不得已才使用這種手法來提高跑分。<br />\n<br />\n退一步來看，如果華為不作弊，那麼在跑分上就會比其他人低，這樣不利於宣傳。但華為作為中國手機龍頭更應該注意名聲和國際形象。"},{"pid":"849fbc43c34f8e68ce3539fcfcabfa0fd95381ed","tid":811543,"uid":202464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"支那野係咁架啦"},{"pid":"4e86dd877a792ef246203f9628915621264dbb82","tid":811543,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"合理"},{"pid":"0a7e8648e3395dcf38f7cdf857cb728f43da1c2d","tid":811543,"uid":205462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"習思想: 不被發現的造假，都是合情合理，合符國情及黨綱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cc9be0f8a8c3c00d3279b82e80fda206638295","tid":811543,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"已為去南極跑分"},{"pid":"a2a8b74d268d2c3f37d20247f0c3ebb52d4ac588","tid":811543,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"佢又冇錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三叔同lg咪又係造假"},{"pid":"a73ab696cc52f872343c44c13ec7a7b62d1dcaee","tid":811543,"uid":83623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a8b74d268d2c3f37d20247f0c3ebb52d4ac588","tid":811543,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"佢又冇錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三叔同lg咪又係造假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"先前benchmark hacking 小米都有做，但之後更新又咪係删咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係主要Huawei 要吹自煮CPU 秒Apple 秒Qualcomm 先係咁多少動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0559aa08fa22c828bad2c87873480f380f0f116f","tid":811543,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5c256e8ab7a94c54f45b04d171ea36e40e8171","tid":811543,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94149f783341a6f4b1175489f8582af584c6a06","tid":811543,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"好奇咩"}]}